  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/875360/extras/48ed0be473edfc88da0b884140a47d1a.avif?t=1643379717\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br>Welcome to the dead world. You are the last alive in this world. Now you are alone against monsters - waves of zombies are going to conquer the whole world. <br><br>Fight against monsters: your goal is to use all your courage and skills to win. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose the weapon according to the kind of zombie: pistol, revolver, sawed-off shotgun and double-barrel shotgun;<br></li><li>Banish all the zombies - you are the only hope of all 9 worlds.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/875360/extras/b2ad44042ea2424928c69e7c966d9c60.avif?t=1643379717\" width=600 height=294 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Exciting zombie survival simulator;<br></li><li>Lots of weapons to prevent zombie assault.</li></ul>",
